trans-unit.source: Identifies a type as an object suitable for binding to an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Identifiserer en type som et objekt som passer for bindingen til en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan arves.

trans-unit.source: Use the DataObjectAttribute attribute to identify an object as suitable for use by an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource> object.
trans-unit.target: Bruk DataObjectAttribute-attributtet til å identifisere et objekt som brukes av en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource>

trans-unit.source: Design-time classes such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ObjectDataSourceDesigner> class use the DataObjectAttribute attribute to present suitable objects to bind to an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource> object.
trans-unit.target: Utformingen klasser som den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ObjectDataSourceDesigner>klassen bruke attributtet DataObjectAttribute presentere passende som skal bindes til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ObjectDataSourceDesigner>

trans-unit.source: For more information about using attributes, see [Attributes](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om hvordan du bruker attributter [attributter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DataObjectAttribute"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DataObjectAttribute"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataObjectAttribute.IsDataObject%2A> property is set to `true` when you use the DataObjectAttribute constructor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataObjectAttribute.IsDataObject%2A>er satt til `true` når du bruker DataObjectAttribute-konstruktøren.</xref:System.ComponentModel.DataObjectAttribute.IsDataObject%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DataObjectAttribute"></xref> class and indicates whether an object is suitable for binding to an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DataObjectAttribute"> </xref> klasse og angir om et objekt som passer for bindingen til en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Use the DataObjectAttribute constructor to indicate to a design-time class such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ObjectDataSourceDesigner> class that an object should be excluded from the list of suitable objects for binding to an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource> object.
trans-unit.target: Bruk DataObjectAttribute-konstruktør som viser til en utformingen klasse som den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ObjectDataSourceDesigner>klasse som et objekt som skal utelates fra listen over passende objekter for bindingen til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ObjectDataSourceDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataObjectAttribute.IsDataObject%2A> property is set to the value of the `isDataObject` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataObjectAttribute.IsDataObject%2A>egenskapen er satt til verdien for den `isDataObject` parameteren.</xref:System.ComponentModel.DataObjectAttribute.IsDataObject%2A>
